(3, 'Support', 'support', '<div class="index">\r\n<section class="wrapper">\r\n<div class="support_sec row">\r\n<aside class="support_left col-md-8">\r\n<hgroup>\r\n<h2>Looking for help? Got a question?</h2>\r\n<h3>We&rsquo;re here to help and we like to respond quickly.</h3>\r\n</hgroup>\r\n<p>Here is how you can get in touch with us, in order of speed:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><strong>Send us an email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@.com">support@milestones.com</a>\r\n<p>This email goes to both Ben, Jeff and Ryan. That means you are guaranteed to get maximum exposure as quickly as possible.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><strong>Call or text us:</strong> <a href="http://112.196.22.164:4107/lapsystem/public/index.php/admin/pages/callto:">+1 504-233-4483</a>\r\n<p>We cannot always answer your call but we&rsquo;ll pick up when we can. If not, please leave us a voicemail with your contact details and some background.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><strong>Twitter:</strong> <a href="#">@bbhive</a>\r\n<p>Not the best way to get direct support but if you must feel free to message us on Twitter, please go ahead. If you really want to get fast support, Tweet about how much you love BumbleBee Child Care Software.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><strong>Message in a bottle:</strong> <em><small><a href="#">(Bottle and cork not included)</a></small></em>\r\n<p>We have offices on both coasts of the United States, so it is possible to get a message to us this way. Is that really the best way if you are using glamourous, web-based <strong>child care software</strong> like BumbleBee Child Care Software?</p>\r\n<div class="customer_support">\r\n<h4>Customers are saying this about our support</h4>\r\n<p><sub>"</sub>BumbleBee has been amazing to work with. Their technical support is astounding!<sub>"</sub></p>\r\n<span>We are aiming equally high with your support request.</span></div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</aside>\r\n<aside class="support_right col-md-4">\r\n<div class="founder">\r\n<h3>Hi! We are the founders of BumbleBee</h3>\r\n<p>We''ll be doing everything we can to help you quickly. Not only are we the founders of <strong>BumbleBee Child Care Software</strong>, we also support, design, develop, market, and sell the product. So you know your request for support will be escalated to the right people.</p>\r\n<figure><img width="75" height="75" src="http://bumblebeehq.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/jeff_150.jpg" /></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="app_status">\r\n<h3>App Status</h3>\r\n<p><strong>We wish you many nines</strong> - Check out <a href="https://status.heroku.com/">platform status.</a> If we are having a service outage, that is the first place to check.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--app_status--></aside>\r\n<!--support_right--></div>\r\n<!--support_sec--></section>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--index-->', '2016-02-09 01:25:38', '2016-05-14 02:00:13'),
(4, 'About Us', 'about-us', '<div class="index">\r\n<section class="wrapper">\r\n<div class="about_sec row">\r\n<h2>About Preschool Managment Software</h2>\r\n<div class="about_mile">\r\n<h4>The Purpose of Our Childcare Software</h4>\r\n<p>BumbleBee <strong>Child Care Software</strong> was created in 2011 to address a fundamental need in society: helping child development professionals focus on developing children.</p>\r\n<p>We cannot do much about actually providing child care, but we can do something about stress and administrative burden of managing a childcare center. Many of the headaches for parents or caregivers come from managing information&hellip; directors want a handle on the whole picture and parents want to know where they stand. Doing so with paper, spreadsheets, phone calls and emails is tough on everyone.</p>\r\n<p>We are focused on making <b>childcare software</b> simple, clear, and affordable.</p>\r\n<div class="about_col_1">\r\n<h4>The Team Behind Your Childcare Center</h4>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-10">\r\n<h3><a href="#" title="Jeff blogs about BumbleBee Childcare Software and other ways to help Childcare Directors and Owners.">Jeff Holden</a></h3>\r\n<p><em>Marketing Director, Shade tree Childcare Software Developer and Bread Baker</em> Jeff is the Marketing Director for BumbleeBee Child Care Software and the only Junior Software developer. Previously, Jeff developed and managed products for major corporations for 15 years. He has a marketing-focused MBA from Carnegie Mellon University. Jeff hangs his hat in The United States in Cambridge, MA (near Boston) and likes <a target="_blank" href="http://www.nytimes.com/2011/03/13/nyregion/13recipe.html?_r=0" title="My favorite recipe for beginners who want to bake excellent bread.">baking bread</a> and canning (in true <a href="https://www.youtube.com/show/portlandia" title="Portlandia is really like this. Not everyone finds Portlandia the show funny, but it''s a great place to visit if you have the chance.">Portlandia</a> fashion) in his spare time. <a rel="me" href="https://plus.google.com/103926176412273333808">Jeff&rsquo;s profile.</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-2">\r\n<figure><img src="http://112.196.22.164:4107/lapsystem/public/assets/images/jef.jpg" alt="Jeff" caption="false" width="150" height="150" /></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-10">\r\n<h3><a href="#" title="Jeff blogs about BumbleBee Childcare Software and other ways to help Childcare Directors and Owners.">Ben Morris</a></h3>\r\n<p><em>Software Development Director, A Double Plus Dad of Two</em><br /> After consulting for seven years to the world&rsquo;s biggest organizations, Ben has turned his management expertise to child care software. Ben used to consult on the thorniest problems, trying to solve road traffic congestion and manage complex technology projects. When Ben is not ridding the world of red tape, he is a father of two adorable children, a web geek, and an amateur photographer.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-2">\r\n<figure><img src="http://112.196.22.164:4107/lapsystem/public/assets/images/ben.jpg" alt="Ben" caption="false" width="150" height="150" /></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--about_col_1-->\r\n<div class="about_col_1">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<h3>The Story Behind our Child Care Software</h3>\r\n<div class="col-md-12">\r\n<p>Back in the summer of 2011, Ben&rsquo;s two children were in daycare with a beautiful center in Washington, DC. The center director had an unusually large waiting list. One thing lead to another and it turned out we thought managing family data for child care centers was something we could help with. It would be something that could benefit childcare administrators and new parents.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<h3>The Story Behind our Name</h3>\r\n<div class="col-md-12">\r\n<p>We wanted something that reflected the underlying product. <a target="_blank" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bumblebee" title="Wikiwepdia entry on bumblebees">Bumblebees are known for being tireless and efficient</a> and that is exactly what we want BumbleBee&rsquo;s childcare management software to be.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--support_sec--></section>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--index-->', '2016-02-15 05:34:12', '2016-02-15 06:29:13'),
(5, 'Customers', 'customers', '<div class="full_title">\r\n<section class="wrapper">\r\n<div class="title_main">\r\n<h1>Join these Standout Child Care Providers</h1>\r\n<span>Experience for yourself how leading early childhood education organizations are managing enrollment</span></div>\r\n</section>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--full_title-->\r\n<div class="index">\r\n<section class="wrapper">\r\n<div class="testimonials_sec">\r\n<div class="testimonail_detail">\r\n<div class="test_logo"><iframe width="170" height="200" src="http://bumblebeehq.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/brown-fox-point-logo.svg"></iframe></div>\r\n<div class="testi_summary">\r\n<h5>Brown/Fox Point</h5>\r\n<span><em>On-campus Childcare for Brown University in Providence, RI</em></span>\r\n<div class="view">\r\n<p>BumbleBee has changed the way Brown/Fox Point manages information, making it easier and faster to get work done.<br /> From the first contact through the end of a</p>\r\n<button type="button" class="btn btn-info" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#demo">SHOW|HIDE</button>\r\n<div id="demo" class="collapse">\r\n<p>family&rsquo;s relationship with our program, BumbleBee assures me that our data is safe and organized in useful ways. Finding a child or family is a snap with the global search, and fast initial entry options allow us to track every contact with ease.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--testimonail_detail-->\r\n<div class="testimonail_detail">\r\n<div class="test_logo"><iframe width="170" height="112" class="alignright size-full wp-image-2114" title="habitat early learning logo" alt="" src="http://bumblebeehq.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/habitat-early-learning-logo1.jpg"></iframe></div>\r\n<div class="testi_summary">\r\n<h5>Habitat Early Learning</h5>\r\n<span><em>Leading Provider of Both Montessori and Traditional Care in Brisbane, Australia </em></span>\r\n<div class="view">\r\n<p>Thanks to BumbleBee our, child care centre now has a paperless, transparent Waiting List system, where parents can feel confident that their applications are being managed effectively.</p>\r\n<button type="button" class="btn btn-info" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#demo">SHOW|HIDE</button>\r\n<div id="demo" class="collapse">\r\n<p>BumbleBee has taken the guesswork out of allocating spots, and we are able to quickly let parents know how they are progressing on our Waiting List. The service and support we have received has also been extraordinary &ndash; we don&rsquo;t know how we ever managed before</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--testimonail_detail-->\r\n<div class="testimonail_detail">\r\n<div class="test_logo"><iframe width="170" height="170" src="http://bumblebeehq.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/escuela-viva.svg"></iframe></div>\r\n<div class="testi_summary">\r\n<h5>Escuela Viva</h5>\r\n<span><em>Vibrant Dual Language Program in Portland, OR</em></span>\r\n<div class="view">\r\n<p>&ldquo;BumbleBee has been amazing to work with. Their technical support is astounding and they are constantly improving the service they offer. We love the ease of managing a large waiting list. Having an electronic waitlist has made our lives so much easier.&rdquo;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--testimonail_detail-->\r\n<div class="testimonail_detail">\r\n<div class="test_logo"><iframe width="i70" height="170" codebase="http://www.adobe.com/svg/viewer/install" type="image/svg+xml" src="http://bumblebeehq.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/sunrise-for-building-enrollment.svg">  </iframe></div>\r\n<div class="testi_summary">\r\n<h5>Your Child Care</h5>\r\n<span><em>Experience the Dawn of Well-designed Software in Anytown, The Globe</em></span>\r\n<div class="view">\r\n<p>Join our other hall of fame users and get on the path to turn more inquiries into enrollments, improve your marketing IQ and spending, and spend more time with children and staff.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--testimonail_detail-->\r\n<div class="section">\r\n<h1>Get Started</h1>\r\n<div class="well-tour">\r\n<div class="well-text-tour">\r\n<h3>Get unlimited access and support without commitment.</h3>\r\n<p>Try BumbleBee free for 30 days and see how easy it is to manage waitlists &amp; enrollment.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="well-button-tour"><a class="reqEval" href="#" title="Try it free today! ">Contact Us to Get Started</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--testimonials_sec--></section>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--index-->', '2016-02-15 07:27:59', '2016-02-15 07:33:16'),
(6, 'Plans', 'plans', '<section class="wrapper">\r\n<div class="pricing_sec">\r\n<div class="pricing_title text-center">\r\n<h2>Plans and Pricing</h2>\r\n<p>Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry''s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n{plans_description} <br />\r\n<div class="text-center view_all"><a href="http://112.196.22.164:4107/lapsystem/public/index.php/features">View All Features</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--pricing_sec-->\r\n<div class="faq_sec">\r\n<h2>Frequently asked questions</h2>\r\n<div class="pull-left faq_list">\r\n<div class="faq_ques">\r\n<h4>What is the difference between a Standard User and Power User?</h4>\r\n<p>Great question. A Standard User has the ability to:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Create Purchase / Expense RequestsReceive</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>A Power User can do all this, plus any combination of the following:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Approve Orders</li>\r\n<li>Create Purchase Orders</li>\r\n<li>Purchase</li>\r\n<li>Admin Privileges</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="faq_ques">\r\n<h4>Can I add or subtract users at any time?</h4>\r\n<p>Yes, you can add or subtract users any time. We wouldn&rsquo;t tell you how to run your business so we want you to structure your account as you like. Your monthly subscription will be pro-rated to reflect any new or subtracted users.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="faq_ques">\r\n<h4>If I stop using Milestones, what happens to my data?</h4>\r\n<p>We&rsquo;re confident we&rsquo;ll keep you happy but if you decide to end the relationship you can export all of your data easily. What you do with your data after you break up with us is none of our business, but we hope you practice safe storage.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--faq_ques--></div>\r\n<div class="pull-right faq_list">\r\n<div class="faq_ques">\r\n<h4>What are my payment options?</h4>\r\n<p>We accept cheques and all major credit cards. We wish we could accept cash but that wouldn&rsquo;t be a good business practice.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="faq_ques">\r\n<h4>Are there hidden fees?</h4>\r\n<p>No! Milestones doesn&rsquo;t believe in hidden fees. We don&rsquo;t charge for implementation, support, new or additional features, updates or maintenance. You can even come visit us for free any time you want and coffee is on us.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="faq_ques">\r\n<h4>Is my data safe?</h4>\r\n<p>Milestones is supported by Amazon Web Services. Your data is fully protected with bank level security and we backup all data every 24 hours. You can even use us to store your personal photos.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--faq_ques-->\r\n<div class="faq_ques">\r\n<h4>How does implementation work?</h4>\r\n<p>Milestones is intuitive purchasing software, designed so you can tailor the system as you like during your trial period. You can import your account codes, vendor lists and budgets and be ready to go in moments. If you get lost or need help, don&rsquo;t worry, we&rsquo;ll walk you through the entire process.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--faq_ques--></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--faq_sec--></section>', '2016-10-01 01:10:45', '2016-10-03 00:16:29'),
